{"tid":609415,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港都有】Apple推iCloud學生優惠　免費200GB年慳$276","createTime":"2018-03-29T04:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T01:01:56.000Z","uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"60ae6eee7bdc39fee37bdc28c16d9b79fcc47300","tid":609415,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"Apple剛在芝加哥舉行了一場針對教育的發佈會，主角是可對應Apple Pencil的新平價9.7吋iPad，教師同學生可以更方便透過iPad教導同學習。不過現時每個Apple ID只得5GB免費iCloud容量，作為教學或學習用途實在唔多夠，好在Apple都特別為教師及學生提供200GB免費iCloud容量，香港亦都適用，不過就要先申請成為「管理式Apple ID」先可得到優惠。200GB iCloud容量本身又值幾錢？以目前iCloud收費，要選用200GB容量的話，月費$23，全年則要$276，雖然唔算好值錢，但對於學生來說實在有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n記者：布偉倫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/123745_e8b8fea947adda6701d4b0827f333022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F123745_e8b8fea947adda6701d4b0827f333022.jpg&h=87c5a69b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54cc9b8c9031e3cbcba777ddd3f7a1c7cedb40b7","tid":609415,"uid":44,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"姐係一般學生都冇用喇"},{"pid":"3a818f5c38b8a9c85cfee41b03c3263da92e10b4","tid":609415,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a36a9c2ec7170064cce2049bf1ba8edc505a60","tid":609415,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"好似話edu尾先得"},{"pid":"5a90e7c1fa9632e4224628f4355ce50f9d87ea3c","tid":609415,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:50:25.000Z","msg":"管理式姐係點？"},{"pid":"13127f78a790d60b6d3c267e8032cc59e88d70af","tid":609415,"uid":30808,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:37:38.000Z","msg":"Google classroom包埋無限容量Google drive<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p