 的使用者提供。如果您是 IT 管理員，請深入瞭解如何使用 Apple School Manager 來管理所屬機構。<br />\n<br />\n教育機構可以為教師和學生建立用於教學的管理式 Apple ID。您的管理式 Apple ID 為所屬機構所有。<br />\n此管理式 Apple ID 具有專屬用途，不同於您為自己建立的其他任何 Apple ID。您可以將您的管理式 Apple ID 與個人 Apple ID 的電子郵件位址和電話號碼建立關聯。與個人 Apple ID 不同的是，您的管理式 Apple ID 可存取的服務是由 IT 管理員負責管理。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle第一條result就係啦 懶撚到閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9624a6d5d0d098c33cbe033b60e96bcfe39546d6","tid":609415,"uid":158225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T17:35:44.000Z","msg":"準備入火坑"},{"pid":"e36c5c1a34f55df175289545ce7249f03686be71","tid":609415,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:44:59.000Z","msg":"算啦我Google Drive都擺咗2TB"},{"pid":"8011094a6dbdc146f0701ddd4fcd89da73f7edac","tid":609415,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d38fe63a3a1b1800b4541d86efe3e30ca3e37049","tid":609415,"uid":101154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"個server 係邊到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:29:50.000Z","msg":"係中國用先俾狗管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5754d6404a0470a2409f89278c168acd290340","tid":609415,"uid":15835,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T22:00:39.000Z","msg":"大學 AC 有無限 Google Drive <br />\n蘋果送俾我都無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0039d9a5a15adbb855963e9e98bde4ae41b2ee01","tid":609415,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T01:17:42.000Z","msg":"Ccccccc"},{"pid":"150f6910a3dfa6bd80df260498d81a569b0f9ce3","tid":609415,"uid":172940,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T01:20:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8433e084159a6b75051b2d66cf441960038e785b","tid":609415,"u